<BR>
Went back. Lulled (Like I should have the first time) and pulled. THat was cake.<BR>
<BR>
One word of advice. If you can, pull to the first ramp. If you pull to the door, the Necros in Bonecrackers room will heal anybody fighting in the doorway.<BR>
<BR>
Hi place holder is a Magician, spawn seemed pretty fast, got the Circlet on the 3rd spawn.<BR>
<BR>
On the Legs themselves... is it just me, or are these just a lil bit crap?<BR>
